title: [Gyldemar Forest, Defile]
description: Blackened rocks form a narrow path that turns sharply to the southwest.  A few blades of grass have conquered the carpet of blackened limbs and grey ash that fills the defile.  Chunks of stone occasionally break loose from the defile's walls.
